      <description>A strange tale whispered among commonfolk: a towering stag with the bulk and hunger of a great bear, said to roam the wilds as one of Hircine’s chosen aspects. Some claim it is the spirit of the hunt given flesh, others that it is a mortal beast twisted by the Daedric Prince’s will.\n\nWhatever its origin, those who cross its path quickly learn that prey and predator are merely roles in Hircine’s eternal game.\n\nThose who emerge victorious may discover the rich, invigorating meat, and after consumption, often feel the thrill of the chase lingering in their blood.</description>
