  <Operation Class="PatchOperationReplace">
    <xpath>/Defs/ThingDef[defName="Seti_loot_letterdaer"]/description</xpath>
    <value>
      <description>An undelivered letter, could be valuable.
            \n\nTo your majesty.
            \nThe reports were true.
            \nThe hunters we sent were taken in the night.
            \nWhat we believed to be some strange beast of the woods
            \nis no mere animal.

            \n\nI tracked the great stag to its cave.
            \nAn elegant creature with great horns,
            \nbut with the bulk and hunger of a bear.
            \nThe locals whisper it is an aspect of the Great Hunt.

            \n\nI watched it drag down a soldier, not ours.
            \nThe creature did not eat him.
            \nIt toyed with him... as if the hunt itself were the purpose.

            \nHe is still alive.
            \nI will attempt to save him
            \nand learn what drives this beast
            \nto hunt with such cruelty.</description>
    </value>
  </Operation>

